snippet.title: CDF GhostShip Review (Early Access) - Worth a Buy?
snippet.description:
CDF Ghostship review, is it Worth a Buy?

CDF Ghostship offers huge replay value and many hours of trigger happy old style FPS fun with Random Events & narrative, Enemies and an open world space ship. With 4 different game modes, expect many hours of sci-fi horror adventure and combat!
